Package: mrfrj
Type: Package
Title: Reversible Jump Monte Carlo Markov Chain for 2-dimensional
  Markov Random Field Interaction Structure Selection
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Victor Freguglia
Maintainer: Victor Freguglia <victorfreguglia@gmail.com>
Description: The package contains the implementation of methods
  proposed in 
  Freguglia & Garcia (2024) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2204.05933>
  for neighborhood selection in 2-dimensional Markov Random Fields
  via Reversible Jump and Pseudoposteriors.
